Ntarindwa Diogene ni umunya[[rwanda]] wavukiye i [[Burundi]] muri 1977, wamenyekanye nka '''Atome''' cyane mu gukina byendagusetsa, ni Umwanditsi  n'umukinnyi wa filimi, ikinamico na comedy. yamenyekanye mu ikinamico nka '''Gasumuni,''' yatangiye gukina ikinamico muri 1994.

== Atome mu gusetsa ==
Atome  gukina amakinamico yabikoze cyane yiga muri kaminuza y'u [[Rwanda]] mu iishami ry'amategeko muri 1996. muri 2002 yagiye gukomeza amasomo i Liege  mu [[Ububiligi]] ibijyanye na Art Dramatique naho akomeza gukina aho yagaragaye mu makinamico arimo Koulsy Lamko, Corpx et voix, Paroles rhizome. muri 2008 yagarutse mu [[Rwanda]] agaragara cyane akina asetsa muri forum yari yateguwe n'Imbuto Foundation Rwanda.

== Atome mu gisirikare ==
'''Atome''' mu rugamba rwo kubohora igihugu 1994 yarimo nk'umusirikare, avuga ko yakigiyem akiri umujene niyompamvu urugamba rurangiye yagiye gukomeza amashuri.
